          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " a low-cost, low-energy method of breaking down some of the most important kinds of ‚Äúforever chemicals‚Äù ‚Äî harmful synthetic compounds previously thought to be indestructible. Project leader William Dichtel told ",
